text: Had an appointment with Master KK and absolutely in love w the results of my eyebrows! I’ve been getting my eyebrow and eyeliner embroidery done by Master Jibby, and she is truly exceptional. Her professionalism and attention to detail are unmatched. She took the time to discuss my preferences, understood my vision, and executed it flawlessly. Highly recommend her for anyone looking for perfection!

I had hairstroke brows done with KK today, and I’m really pleased with the experience. He was super gentle and patient throughout the session, and he would occasionally check in to ensure I was comfortable with the pain level. Highly recommended!
